1. Install the prel modeules  manually or using an repo
     perl-5.16.3-292.el7.x86_64.rpm
     perl-Data-Dumper-2.145-3.el7.x86_64.rpm
2. Extract the tar file in /
     ERICstorapi.tar
3. Install the navicli & hostagent rpms 
     HostAgent-Linux-64-x86-en_US-1.3.9.1.0155-1.x86_64.rpm
     navicli-7.33.1.0.33.rpm
4. Disable the firewall in linux 
    /bin/systemctl stop firewalld.service
5. Hostagent restart
    /etc/rc.d/init.d/hostagent stop/start
6. Use input file as required 
